ssroom environment of paid services, it compensates by offering equal access to high-quality content and practice materials.\n\nFor students who are self-motivated and comfortable with independent study, Khan Academy presents an unmatched value proposition. Its proven effectiveness, as demonstrated by College Board data, confirms that it is a worthy option for those aiming to enhance their math skills and perform well on the SAT.\n\nUltimately, Khan Academy math SAT prep democratizes access to quality test preparation and continues to be a vital tool for millions of students seeking to navigate the college admissions process with confidence.",
